claim.claim-text:
A lane departure warning device comprising:
a compartment line detection unit (1) that detects a compartment line (31, 32) in an image of a running lane (30) on which a vehicle is traveling, the image being captured by an image capturing device (101) which the vehicle has;
a dirtiness detection unit (2) that detects dirtiness on any one of a lens of the image capturing device (101) or a partition between an outside of a vehicle interior of the vehicle and the image capturing device (101);
a departure judgment unit (3) that judges whether or not the vehicle departs from the compartment line (31, 32); and
a warning judgment unit (5) that when it is judged that the vehicle departs from the compartment line (31, 32), outputs a warning signal based on a degree of the dirtiness detected, wherein
a position of the vehicle with respect to the compartment line (31, 32) when the warning signal is output varies depending on the degree of the dirtiness.
